"``10.2.10.4,10.2.10.5``: abilita il port forward solo per il traffico "
"proveniente dagli IP 10.2.10.4 e 10.2.10.5"

#: ../../firewall.rst:228
msgid ""
"``10.2.10.0/24``: enable port forward only for traffic coming from "
"10.2.10.0/24 network"
msgstr ""
"``10.2.10.0/24``: abilita il port forward solo per il traffico proveniente "
"dalla rete 10.2.10.0/24"

#: ../../firewall.rst:229
msgid "``!10.2.10.4``: enable port forward  for all IPs except 10.2.10.4"
msgstr ""
"``!10.2.10.4``: abilita il port forward per tutti gli IP tranne 10.2.10.4"

